				<name>Aḷaka / Mūḷaka</name>
				<description><![CDATA[A country on the banks of the Godhāvarī River. It was at a spot between the territories of the Alaka and the Assaka kings that Bāvarī lived. <span class="ref">Snp.977</span> To the north of Alaka was Patiṭṭhāna. <span class="ref">Snp.1011</span>]]></description>
