				<name>Gandhāra</name>
				<description><![CDATA[One of the sixteen Great Nations.<span class="ref">AN.i.213</span><span class="ref">AN.iv.252</span> One of the teeth of the Buddha was deposited in Gandhāra. <span class="ref">DN.ii.167</span>]]></description>
