			<Placemark>
				<name>Jantugāma</name>
				<description><![CDATA[A village near Cālikā; close by was the river Kimikālā with the mango-grove on its banks. Meghiya, while staying with the Buddha at Cālikā, once went to Jantugāma for alms. <span class="ref">AN.iv.354</span><span class="ref">Ud.iv.1</span>]]></description>
