				<name>Vanasavhaya / Vanasa / Vanasāvhaya / Tumbavanagara / Pavana / Vanasāvatthī</name>
				<description><![CDATA[A city lying between Vedisa and Kosambī, on the road taken by Bāvarī’s disciples. <span class="ref">Snp.1011</span>]]></description>
