			<Placemark>
				<name>Vebhāra</name>
				<description><![CDATA[One of the five hills surrounding Rājagaha. <span class="ref">MN.iii.68</span> In this hill was the Sattapaṇṇiguhā, where the first Convocation was held. <span class="ref">Vin.ii.76</span> The river Tapodā rose in a lake at the foot of Vebhāra.]]></description>
				<styleUrl>#icon-503-DB4436</styleUrl>
